{
 "base_path": "/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam70001",
 "body": "<div><br /></div>\n<p>HMRC is committed to delivering high standards of customer service, as set out in The HMRC Charter. The Charter explains what people, businesses and organisations can expect from HMRC, as well as what HMRC expects from them. For further information, see <span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW250608990 BCX8\"><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hmrc-charter/the-hmrc-charter\">The HMRC Charter - GOV.UK</a></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW250608990 BCX8\">Customers who require extra support, or need information in an alernative format, can find further details through the following GOV.UK pages:</span></p>\n<div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW197674289 BCX8\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hmrc-charter/hmrcs-principles-of-support-for-customers-who-need-extra-help--3\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW197674289 BCX8\">HMRC’s principles of support for customers who need extra help - GOV.UK</span></span></a><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW197674289 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW197674289 BCX8\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/get-help-hmrc-extra-support\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW197674289 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW197674289 BCX8\">Get help from HMRC if you need extra support: Help<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW197674289 BCX8\">you can get - GOV.UK</span></span></a><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW197674289 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div><br /></div>\n",
